CarInfo: The BMW 330e brings the combination of BMW’s electric motor and the TwinPower Turbo 4-cylinder petrol engine puts the BMW 330e Plug-in Hybrid in a league of its own. Offering a combined range of 372 miles and a 0 to 62mph acceleration of just 6.5 seconds – it’s time to rediscover The Ultimate Driving Machine as a plug-in hybrid (PHEV).
